gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n益你啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/001546_7c9f3a74813078c1a9ea133ef1ccf075.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F001546_7c9f3a74813078c1a9ea133ef1ccf075.gif&h=75ca2a8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f48ba47e2cdc67582ca0fa381a883e57da079f69","tid":45274,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"肥婆搭地鐵應該俾雙倍<br />\n<br />\n第一，臭 其他人要忍受肥婆體味<br />\n第二，佔用較多車廂位置 造成逼夾<br />\n第三，視覺上影響觀感 令乘客感到不安<br />\n第四，體重 直接影響機件問題 增加工程開支<br />\n<br />\n其他 歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b2c6e41b68c6a449ee2f455716d73f12f5a411","tid":45274,"uid":35010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"根本地鐵個位就唔係design比肥婆坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9d5413fa39b439fd5ef9260dea8b5f051baa92","tid":45274,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"肉貼肉真係好噁心"},{"pid":"42709eb63905e57ccdfa90d129521cafd72caf29","tid":45274,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本地鐵個位就唔係design比肥婆坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥婆應該好似燒味咁拎個勾掛係上邊扶手"},{"pid":"b708dc86cd6ad8ff6d34f32cfe4c72713482d724","tid":45274,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"肥婆嘅存在 本身就係一種罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"5e6cca2b6e9cba2e61bf4646fd9b88a4d2439ec7","tid":45274,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"sorry lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc <img src=\"/asset